
Install gh using apt-get or brew
Set up authentication using "gh auth login"
-or-
Set GITHUB_TOKEN

Wrangler tool:

Seal spec. (Ensure sha256 and/or signing complete)
Create a unique dated submission branch.
Copy spec to clone’s injest directory. Create dir if needed.
Add spec.
Commit spec. Compose commit message from spec.

Push submission branch.
PR the submission branch to main


Ingest Workflow:

Validate branch diffs and identify added spec.
Validate spec.
Configure env for spec’s deployment name.
Copy spec to archive branch.
Delete spec from ingest dir.
Inject spec into deployment code.
